# --- Recommended on Vercel (no VITE_ needed): ---
# Set ONLY in Vercel Dashboard → Environment Variables (server-side):
#   RAILWAY_API_BASE_URL=https://your-service.up.railway.app
# The UI calls same-origin /api/*; Vercel proxies to Railway (see frontend/api/[...slug].ts).
#
# --- Optional: direct browser → Railway (skip proxy) ---
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-service.up.railway.app
#
# --- Local dev: point Vite proxy at Railway if backend not on localhost ---
# RAILWAY_API_BASE_URL=https://your-service.up.railway.app
